" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T05:52:23.000Z","msg":"唔該*"},{"pid":"ddeeae6336711507c3181da8988c3ecafe3fe896","tid":1040314,"uid":80814,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"其實真正目標係YG同喺背後嘅人<br />\n勝利點睇都似係白手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11810c1be20c5b76c604f2ad16a4a2ebd100827f","tid":1040314,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T06:07:49.000Z","msg":"TL?"},{"pid":"aa677d40a0813138ecf80a815fa09410a9794937","tid":1040314,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 揚威海外"},{"pid":"c58b5d38e5349e5f4ad4e41ba040c2be0eb7a297","tid":1040314,"uid":63057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T06:51:52.000Z","msg":"Jackson?"},{"pid":"8c37afc02de4f11b0bcfebf8dc12db7b263aefe3","tid":1040314,"uid":51793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11810c1be20c5b76c604f2ad16a4a2ebd100827f","tid":1040314,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T06:07:49.000Z","msg":"TL?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:37:06.000Z","msg":"Party with TL<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4b10bf74b959acdc5025a4381ac00e9cee7831","tid":1040314,"uid":51793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c58b5d38e5349e5f4ad4e41ba040c2be0eb7a297","tid":1040314,"uid":63057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T06:51:52.000Z","msg":"Jackson?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:37:39.000Z","msg":"佢支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且佢老豆邊係富豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ab373ef2c6a94060a34dc79e542ab7881fa43f","tid":1040314,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T08:04:28.000Z","msg":"喪清黎"},{"pid":"f80024a17a7b43ddc28da75c0102ec008efe1852","tid":1040314,"uid":137470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"啲情節好睇過拍戲"}]}